update.notes:
JEM 4.4.1 for Joomla! 4.4.x and Joomla! 5.x;
        If you are upgrading from JEM 2.x and Joomla 3 and use template overrides please note that all views have been changed and there is a good chance that your overrides won't work as expected.;
            So please check the changes and adapt your files.;
            For migration from JEM on Joomla 3.10.x, don't uninstall, only disable plugin and modules. Versions previous to 2.3.5 will not migrate correctly.

update.changes:
JEM 4.4.1 was released on February 23, 2026;
        Fix a bug of access fields in JEM tables and set default value to 1 (Public);
        An other minor fixes;
        Please refer to the changelog for details.
